snippet.title: Paralegal Reacts To AMBER HEARD TESTIMONY in JOHNNY DEPP V. NGN
snippet.description:
PARALEGAL REACTS TO JOHNNY DEPP V. AMBER HEARD

I reacted to Amber Heard’s testimony day 1, via Nick Wallis’ live tweets. Unfortunately he won’t be doing this anymore, but you can read the past tweets as well as he will be posting transcripts. Follow his twitter below if you want to read for yourself or stay up to date! 

Nick Wallis: https://mobile.twitter.com/nickwallis

Also gonna link Lost Beyond Pluto, who is a lawyer who breaks down the legality of this case very professionally: https://www.youtube.com/c/lostbeyondpluto

Link to Incredibly Average, he has covered this case in depth from beginning to very recently.. including animated re-enactments etc. Highly recommend!: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ

Thank you so much for the love on my last video I really appreciate it! I hope this was helpful or enjoyable in some way. I plan to keep up with this case so stay tuned and make sure you are subscribed!

Apologies for all the jump cuts, it was a lot of footage so I tried to cut out as many pauses as I could, as short as they were. and I apologize if the screen recording doesn’t line up exact to my video. 

Email: Debidooms@gmail.com
Instagram: debidoesmakeup
TikTok: debidooms

DISCLAIMER:: This video is all my OPINION based on public information on this case. Please do not take anything I say as fact and come to your own conclusions based on the evidence presented.
